            "title": "融創中國遭入稟清盤 排期3月中審理",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"內房地產商融創中國遭入稟清盤，案件3月中審理。資料圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/ea52cf799171842d9a23a148e199fc7b/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250110/_2025011011441875271.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">內房地產商融創中國遭入稟清盤，案件3月中審理。資料圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>內地大型房地產商融創中國控股有限公司疑出現財困，昨遭債權人中國信達(香港)資產管理有限公司入稟高等法院呈請清盤。根據司法機構網頁紀錄，聆訊排期於3月19日上午9時半審理。\n\n</p>\n<p>案件編號：HCCW16/2025\n\n</p>\n<p>法庭記者：陳子豪\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2046282/即時-港聞-融創中國遭入稟清盤-排期3月中審理",
            "pub_date": "2025-01-10 11:45:55",
