            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"7旬婦捱的士撞，清醒送院。劉漢權攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/ddb1b6d2920e6056a3aeb352a89fbd61/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250110/_2025011011411495394.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">7旬婦捱的士撞，清醒送院。劉漢權攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>旺角通菜街與界限街交界，今（10日）早上10時48分，一部的士沿界限街東行，駛至近通菜街斑馬線期間，撞倒一名70多歲女途人，女途人盤骨受傷，清醒送院治理。的士司機在場協查。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4008866/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"旺角通菜街與界限街交界的士撞女途人。劉漢權攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/76cd0256935d7996acd62d421cbafdfb/2025-01/KakaoTalk_20250110_112408140_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        旺角通菜街與界限街交界的士撞女途人。劉漢權攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4008867/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"的士沿界限街向東行，駛至近通菜街斑馬線期間，撞倒70多歲女途人。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/eb2e183b3b1efba775d614c60339d2f9/2025-01/KakaoTalk_20250110_112408140_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library